data.description: Check out this 3 BDR / 2 BTH home located in the Check / Pilot area of Floyd County. Over 1,200 sq ft, this home complete with a permanent foundation is located on over 4 very usable wooded acres. The property has two entrances: Coles Knob and Ridge Rd. New interior flooring throughout home, gas range in kitchen. Home is heated by heat pump as well as outdoor wood stove which DOES convey. The detached garage with concrete floor is connected to the outdoor wood stove as well as having it's own split mini unit installed. Property totals 4.05 acres made of two adjacent individual tracts - possibility of new owner always having the option to then sale the adjacent 2 acre tract could exist. Call today and set your appointment!
